The City of El Paso, in collaboration with @UTEP and the Texas Military Department, will be opening two additional COVID-19 testing sites tomorrow, Wednesday, Oct. 21.

The two new testing sites will be located at the UTEP Schuster 1 Parking Lot and the Eastside Sports Complex.
